{"tid":2221092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華為曾向台積電訂1500萬顆 Kirin 9000，最終只能交出約一半數量","createTime":"2020-09-28T06:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T12:31:51.000Z","uid":25468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"19068d7f5bc866a87dd151192b1e7bd8351a02d5","tid":2221092,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T06:28:53.000Z","msg":"隨著美國對華為的禁令開始生效，台積電已經無法向華為代工，華為手機的未來將會這麼樣呢？Kirin 處理器還會有迭代嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/LkoVIcGGg8pZjbyGEpyNYQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/iloveapps.com/f174c0c294fd6ad07a265932e69488eb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FLkoVIcGGg8pZjbyGEpyNYQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Filoveapps.com%2Ff174c0c294fd6ad07a265932e69488eb&h=ef8a133c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據國外媒體的消息，可以得知華為即將發布的 Mate 40 系列將搭載 Kirin 9000 處理器，採用台積電 5nm 工藝代工。可惜的是，自從9月15日禁令生效之後，台積電就已經停止向華為代工處理器了。<br />\n<br />\n在之前，有媒體報導華為向台積電下了多達 1500萬顆的處理器訂單，可謂是多多益善。但是截止到9月15日，台積電生產多少還是未知數。推測只有880萬顆左右已交貨。<br />\n<br />\n在8月份召開的中國信息化百人會2020年峰會上，華為消費者業務 CEO 余承東曾發表演講稱，華為 Mate 40 系列所搭載的 Kirin 處理器很可能是華為自產的最後一代，這此之後<strong><span class=\"limegreen\"> Kirin 處理器將變成絕版</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.style.yahoo.com/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%9B%BE%E5%90%91%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB%E8%A8%821500%E8%90%AC%E9%A1%86-kirin-9000-%E6%9C%80%E7%B5%82%E5%8F%AA%E4%BA%A4%E5%87%BA-134211986.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.style.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%25A9%258D%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A8%25821500%25E8%2590%25AC%25E9%25A1%2586-kirin-9000-%25E6%259C%2580%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%258F%25AA%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%2587%25BA-134211986.html&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIXr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=43a74a01\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.style.yahoo.com/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%9B%BE%E5%90%91%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB%E8%A8%821500%E8%90%AC%E9%A1%86-kirin-9000-%E6%9C%80%E7%B5%82%E5%8F%AA%E4%BA%A4%E5%87%BA-134211986.html</a>"},{"pid":"e7b88177599fc6e7e592f93bd88f4699c34057fb","tid":2221092,"uid":286146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:34:01.000Z","msg":"比夠1億粒晶片華為都冇用<br />\n要收皮既點都係會收皮"},{"pid":"6fe1187570643c4b8701c7ac773a127658fd4f84","tid":2221092,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7b88177599fc6e7e592f93bd88f4699c34057fb","tid":2221092,"uid":286146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:34:01.000Z","msg":"比夠1億粒晶片華為都冇用<br />\n要收皮既點都係會收皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:44:53.000Z","msg":"想 keep 住條生產線拖到美國大選之後搏翻身 , 生產線一停要 rebuild 翻會麻煩好多"},{"pid":"0995e9bf84a666b62d5660c649535e9d9ac68c17","tid":2221092,"uid":226851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7b88177599fc6e7e592f93bd88f4699c34057fb","tid":2221092,"uid":286146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:34:01.000Z","msg":"比夠1億粒晶片華為都冇用<br />\n要收皮既點都係會收皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:43:35.000Z","msg":"挨多個幾月就解禁啦，應該夠用嘅。"},{"pid":"8f6a597e7e74aa6644a50debdedf68afccca40bd","tid":2221092,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:31:51.000Z","msg":"乘機派兵佔領？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}